# Cursor Rules

## Auto-Knowledge Graph

Before starting work, ALWAYS read these files first:

1. `AGENTS.md` - Agent rules and auto-update instructions
2. `.understand-anything/knowledge-graph.json` - Full project architecture (274 nodes, 338 edges)
3. `.understand-anything/PROJECT_AUDIT.md` - Human-readable project audit

## After Code Changes

Run this command to keep the knowledge graph updated:
```bash
node scripts/quick-update.mjs
```

This takes ~30 seconds and updates the project map.
